{"tid":909096,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"到底係一次不忠百次不容 定 百次不用","createTime":"2018-11-20T06:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T07:28:38.000Z","uid":17088,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6d7576598805c13e9176a4a69a1084b70636e4f4","tid":909096,"uid":17088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T06:05:35.000Z","msg":"喺隔離post係咁見到百次不用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明細個用開百次不容<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080fa2d32bce969a516d9224901dfc4f02e19d2c","tid":909096,"uid":176445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6d7576598805c13e9176a4a69a1084b70636e4f4","tid":909096,"uid":17088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T06:05:35.000Z","msg":"喺隔離post係咁見到百次不用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明細個用開百次不容<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T06:10:27.000Z","msg":"孟加拉效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880700d97d33cd7acfff2eb7a6a2af6a48329ac3","tid":909096,"uid":214016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T06:10:36.000Z","msg":"單從表面看來，似乎「用」和「容」都解得通，不過正確的用法應是「一次不忠，百次不用」。這裏「用」字的解釋，似乎被大家誤解了。 <br />\n<br />\n「用」字除了平日常用的「使用，施行」之義，還可以解作「效勞，出力」的。《商君書．靳令》：「六蝨成群，則民不用」，《商君書》指國家若有「六蝨」，人民便不効忠國家，國家便趨弱。《商君書》的道理如何，這裏不作深論。要之，「用」字若作「效勞，出力」之義，當然不能跟「容」字互換。 <br />\n<br />\n「一次不忠，百次不用」是指「某人曾有一次不盡忠，他以後一百次便有一百次不盡忠」，所以我們不再任用他。如果是「一次不忠，百次不容」的話，則變成「某人曾有一次不盡忠，（我）便有一百次不容他」，這樣是解不通的。「一不忠，百不容」尚可解釋，但加上一「次」字後，只能用「一次不忠，百次不用」了。"},{"pid":"83c0a0a8e4389276a180088df46d0bd089b705fa","tid":909096,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:01:03.000Z","msg":"綠野仙蹤 定 淥嘢先中？"},{"pid":"5dfdfa1251d498b79f3a7e41e26fac7e5693023c","tid":909096,"uid":185176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"83c0a0a8e4389276a180088df46d0bd089b705fa","tid":909096,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:01:03.000Z","msg":"綠野仙蹤 定 淥嘢先中？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:10:16.000Z","msg":"係咪好笑姐？"},{"pid":"c032d0bee4866528e36bb418c5e54d480d404450","tid":909096,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:14:18.000Z","msg":"又黎冚家拉效應"},{"pid":"099f2c9f477dd78472c77ca328774f8d0c1b31d2","tid":909096,"uid":17088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"080fa2d32bce969a516d9224901dfc4f02e19d2c","tid":909096,"uid":176445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6d7576598805c13e9176a4a69a1084b70636e4f4","tid":909096,"uid":17088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T06:05:35.000Z","msg":"喺隔離post係咁見到百次不用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明細個用開百次不容<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T06:10:27.000Z","msg":"孟加拉效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:27:39.000Z","msg":"咪on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a02ce969d0cae5dbcd2f2be0a3162b9973b1fe","tid":909096,"uid":17088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c032d0bee4866528e36bb418c5e54d480d404450","tid":909096,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:14:18.000Z","msg":"又黎冚家拉效應"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:28:02.000Z","msg":"唔撚係呀"},{"pid":"1bf429de39055798d795072d861c9ffa12d95315","tid":909096,"uid":17088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83c0a0a8e4389276a180088df46d0bd089b705fa","tid":909096,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:01:03.000Z","msg":"綠野仙蹤 定 淥嘢先中？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:28:38.000Z","msg":"鹿死誰手定淥死誰手?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}